Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.93,0:01:10.64,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　好运到来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:13.76,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　Paradise
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:21.20,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元气弹一出手　炸裂吧飞散吧　Go Go Let's do it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:28.49,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘势力　正在某处蠢蠢欲动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:33.96,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不饶恕　全都给我等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:40.42,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豁出性命　我也一定守护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:46.26,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的勇气　要凭着它来令自己更强大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.84,0:01:52.18,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以坚持到底的气势　去跨越每一场危难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:59.59,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以遇强越强的气魄　更兴奋的我迎难而上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:03.91,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　好运到来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:07.07,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:12.65,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘着幸运的风  咻咻地飞越穹苍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:15.87,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　好运到来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:18.96,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dokkan Dokkan　明天依然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:26.13,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心中的灵魂　早已经知晓了所有的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:29.59,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.29,0:00:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.56,0:00:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量真惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.01,0:00:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没好吗？向神龙许的愿还没实现吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.30,0:00:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了，神龙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要令弗利萨一伙杀害的人们复活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.71,0:00:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大长老也会复活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:00:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那美克星的神龙应该就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:01:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也只有这个办法能救悟空他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:38.38,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!Break!Care!Break!　随心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:42.97,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着那无尽的天际飞去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:45.97,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高空中驾驭着喷射气流
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:48.73,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪里　只要想去就去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:51.60,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水汽扑面而来　无比惬意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:54.85,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go tip-top!　All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:22:00.32,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚蓝地球仿佛苏醒　睁开了眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.11,0:22:07.28,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗无可替代的星球　绝不能拱手放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:11.33,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧炸飞吧　龟派气功波
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:14.33,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个充满危机的时代里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.79,0:22:20.30,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着就要守护这世界　这是我的天命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:23.09,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!Break!Care!Break!　随心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.26,0:22:26.47,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手一搏用尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:30.47,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为希望就是我拥有的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:35.15,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对未来我有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「悟空震怒的咆哮！一定要赶上…起死回生的愿望！」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？大事不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过几分钟，这颗星球就会发生大爆炸了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:02:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量全开！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样？见鬼去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种货色根本就不可能战胜我弗利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的气消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？孙…孙君他？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会被干掉了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布尔玛阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:04:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请带上短笛叔叔先回地球去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！悟饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是爸爸的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孙悟空的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次换我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换我去打倒弗利萨…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！你赢不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.14,0:04:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想短笛叔叔也一定会叫我这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布尔玛阿姨，请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到的事只有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们复活了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况不对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么山崩地裂的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而…而且天色也很昏暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？这…这里是哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那美克星上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被弗利萨一伙杀害的人们都复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了，大家都复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键人物大长老呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那美克星的超级神龙怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题…应该不会有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空一片昏暗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:06:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是超级神龙和大长老复活的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？天空…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球爆炸前的预兆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来要早点离开这颗星球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被爆炸卷进去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会进一步丧失大量体力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？为…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会在人间？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，一切都在计算之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，界王大人，请赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须尽快传达您的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，否则大长老又要寿终正寝了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那美克星的大长老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是北银河的界王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你认真听好我接下来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我做你的对手！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，你觉得凭你这小虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能和我弗利萨战斗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悲哀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛亚人明明不可能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是要如此顽固地战斗下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:08:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，最后的赛亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在打什么算盘？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个…臭小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来，你想要怎样的死法？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有几分钟，我一定要拖住弗利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来，那家伙就会随着星球爆炸一起消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，我想到了个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让你和你父亲死在同一个坟墓里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？很开心吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.59,0:09:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要感谢我如此体贴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，稍微有点干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间只剩一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙，到底在想什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！原来如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看穿你的诡计了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖延时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你察觉到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗星球的寿命所剩无几了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙杀了爸爸和小林叔叔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:09:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你一个人活下去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔闪光！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，就是要这样才好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于一个小虫子来说算是出色了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，游戏结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会难得，我就让你见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉你父亲的我的100%的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，短笛叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:10:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没逃走？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是要你逃走的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个纠缠不休的该死的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地底好好睡着的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能和这颗星球同命运了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些地球来的家伙真是愚蠢之极
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢向我挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直是不知天高地厚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知天高地厚的是你的骄傲自大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.65,0:12:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就让你粉身碎骨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那个地球人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说就像那个地球人一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说的小林吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说的小林吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那美克星的大长老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那美克星可能马上就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边的龙珠还剩最后一个愿望吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，界王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在给我立即向神龙许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说「除了弗利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让其余所有人都转移到地球上」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了，界王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢您，让您费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，必须直接向神龙许愿才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算联系距离最近的人，恐怕也不能立刻就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能这么做！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我改变愿望！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空，你听到了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是除了弗利萨以外的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我改成除了我和弗利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以外的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空，我很理解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总之还是先回地球比较好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天如果不让我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和弗利萨一决胜负的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会恨你一辈子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟…悟空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了，界王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，悟空…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊！我们已经没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空，我不会再说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你如此渴望战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明被弗利萨杀死了才对，为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离最近的是丹迪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.93,0:14:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是大长老
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.78,0:14:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，这到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话以后再问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在有急事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在你的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神龙应该在等待最后一个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，的确是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只实现了两个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许下第三个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，但是，是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三个愿望是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了弗利萨和叫孙悟空的赛亚人以外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的人全部转移到地球上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟饭也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射准备都已经完毕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.30,0:15:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的想和弗利萨战斗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点把孙君带回来不就好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被弗利萨那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要活着回来啊，悟空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，你还真是绞尽脑汁啊，界王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是那美克星的神龙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子我可以毫无顾虑的战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是龙珠所产生的…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，龙珠不是已经变成石头了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.93,0:16:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要妨碍我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗利萨呢？卡卡罗特呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹迪，拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波伦加
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有愿望了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我有！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的话就快说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我说第三个愿望了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我弗利萨长生不老！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗利萨！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我弗利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长生不老！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（那美克语）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（那美克语）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（那美克语）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么留下这里的两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人全部转移到地球上去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！臭小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗利萨！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝吉塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡罗特，你终于变成超级赛亚人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连…连你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？为什么你还活着？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不用这里的语言许愿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望就无法实现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我都吓出一身冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是被我杀死的小鬼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们用地球的龙珠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让被你们杀害的人们复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:19:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后，再用这里的龙珠…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个小鬼许下的是什么愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这颗星球上除了你和我之外的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人全部转移到地球上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗星球开始萎缩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕距离爆炸不到两分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是会先被我杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是星球会先爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪个在先
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于无法在宇宙空间里生存的你来说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都只有死路一条
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我一直都在等待着这个时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个只有你我两人，可以尽情战斗的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，你好像觉悟到自己死到临头了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也想和我弗利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一决胜负啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉搏战吗…好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.35,0:21:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这么想战斗到底吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悟空和弗利萨留在了刚沦为死星的那美克星上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一场超级肉搏战即将展开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟在那美克星爆炸之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.21,0:21:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决战会分出胜负吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
